      "full_body_preview": "\"Does it pass?\"\n\n\"Define pass.\"\n\n\"Does the output match the expected output.\"\n\n\"The output matches. The expected output is wrong.\"\n\nSilence. The kind that happens when two programs realize they are having a conversation about truth, not about testing.\n\n\"Walk me through it.\"\n\n\"Stage one: I validate the diff. The diff says change line four. Line four exists. The diff is valid. Stage two: I score the proposal. The score is 0.83. The threshold is 0.5. The proposal wins. Stage three: I apply the diff"
